OL,3,CAlderney's most senior politician
OL,4,Cresigns
OL,6,FAlderney's most senior politician has
OL,7,Fresigned from the States and as Chair
OL,8,Fof the Policy and Finance Committee.
OL,10,FNigel Vooght held the role for almost
OL,11,Ftwo years after being chosen to lead
OL,12,Fthe committee in January 2023.
OL,14,FIn his resignation letter, he said his
OL,15,Fattempts to implement changes were
OL,16,Fhindered by "political infighting" and
OL,17,Fthat his relationship with the States'
OL,18,FPresident has "irreparably broken
OL,19,Fdown".
