OL,3,CAlderney's most senior politician
OL,4,Cresigns
OL,6,FHe said: "I entered the States two
OL,7,Fyears ago in full awareness that there
OL,8,Fwere tough decisions to be made, and
OL,9,Fat no stage have I ever expected to
OL,10,Fwin a personality contest in helping
OL,11,Fto reach those decisions.
OL,13,F"My intention and motive were simply
OL,14,Fto get things done."
OL,16,FHe added that Alderney has "so much
OL,17,Fpotential" but claims the island won't
OL,18,Fachieve what it deserves as its
OL,19,Fpoliticians are "so divided and
OL,20,Fconsistently attempt to belittle
OL,21,Fothers who are trying their hardest."
