OL,3,CAlderney's most senior politician
OL,4,Cresigns
OL,6,FHe wished the States well but made a
OL,7,Fplea to its members to focus on
OL,8,Fexternal issues rather than fighting
OL,9,Famongst themselves.
OL,11,FIn response to the announcement,
OL,12,FAlderney's Chief Executive Theo
OL,13,FLeijser said: "Real progress has been
OL,14,Fmade over the past year in reaching
OL,15,Fimportant decisions and taking steps
OL,16,Fto repair the political relationship
OL,17,Fwith Guernsey."
