OL,6,FHe added: "Mr Vooght has worked
OL,7,Ftirelessly to seek solutions to our
OL,8,FAirport runway crisis and has proudly
OL,9,Frepresented the island in top-flight
OL,10,Fdelegations in Guernsey, the Bailiwick
OL,11,Fand further afield."
OL,13,FA by-election to fill his role will be
OL,14,Fheld in the New Year.
